  {'source_id': 1, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:05Z', 'title': 'Experimentation on Vampires (Book)', 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/Experimentation_on_Vampires_%28Book%29', 'text': 'The captured vampires were quite young, only a few nights old. They were of no value concerning information about their secret society. Nonetheless two of them were given to the torturers. As expected...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 2, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:34Z', 'title': "About Antarel's Family Line (Book)", 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/About_Antarel%27s_Family_Line_(Book)', 'text': 'The family line of the Antarel family was tainted with orcish blood since generations. A shameful secret hidden from the public. Though thought to have thinned out enough to no longer pose a threat, t...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 3, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:35Z', 'title': 'About Count Vlarkorth (Book)', 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/About_Count_Vlarkorth_(Book)', 'text': 'Vlarkorth was a wandering hero even in his youth. Heroic quests lead him all over the world and perhaps even beyond. Sometimes in his travels, while he already was a well-known and established knight,...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 4, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:35Z', 'title': 'About Duke Krule (Book)', 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/About_Duke_Krule_(Book)', 'text': 'Duke Krule was born into a zealous family of thaian nobility. His oppressive and pious upbringing suited him well and from early age he joined an order of knights, dedicated to erase anything they dee...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 5, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:36Z', 'title': 'About Joining the Inquisition (Book)', 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/About_Joining_the_Inquisition_(Book)', 'text': 'Only the most pious are allowed to join our ranks. The churches support the inquisition in their efforts to get rid of heretics that try to undermine our society. They are an illness and we are the cu...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 6, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:36Z', 'title': 'About Lord Azaram (Book)', 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/About_Lord_Azaram_(Book)', 'text': 'The songs of Azaram were numerous and several of them lived on to be still sung in our days. His chivalrous exploits were the base of many modern fairy tales and three of the lections of the art of fi...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 7, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:36Z', 'title': 'About Luthgar Decars (Book)', 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/About_Luthgar_Decars_(Book)', 'text': 'The individual that was researching vampire lore and especially the whereabouts of possible vampires or their remains was NOT acting on behalf of the inquisition. In the light of warnings about some s...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 8, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:37Z', 'title': 'About Magnor Mournbringer (Book)', 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/About_Magnor_Mournbringer_(Book)', 'text': 'Magnor Mournbringer was more a mystic and philosopher than a knight. It is said he was forced into knighthood by his father, albeit himself aspiring to become a sorcerer. He was more a man of the book...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 9, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:37Z', 'title': 'About Nargol the Impaler (Book)', 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/About_Nargol_the_Impaler_(Book)', 'text': 'Nargol the impaler was a disgraced knight of an unimportant noble family. Acts of cowardice and drunken violence had cost him any of the little reputation that his birth right and knighthood had given...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 10, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:38Z', 'title': 'About Rewar the Bloody (Book)', 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/About_Rewar_the_Bloody_(Book)', 'text': 'Rewar the bloody was a petty man of intrigue with the aspiration to become king. Through manipulation and deception he acquired a great deal of power. To raise his status he claimed several heroic dee...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 11, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:39Z', 'title': "About the Shiron'Fal (Book)", 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/About_the_Shiron%27Fal_(Book)', 'text': "The Shiron'Fal was created while the god wars were most intense. It was a gathering of generals that oversaw the course of battle. Each of them a mastermind of immense power. Yet even they were unable...", 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 12, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:39Z', 'title': "About the Shiron'Fal II (Book)", 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/About_the_Shiron%27Fal_II_(Book)', 'text': "The assumption that the organisation Shiron'Fal had a hand in the exposure and ultimately destruction of two members of the triangle of terror seems rather unlikely. The effective elimination of the c...", 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 13, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:40Z', 'title': "About the Shiron'Fal III (Book)", 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/About_the_Shiron%27Fal_III_(Book)', 'text': "Shiron'Fal Ancient organisation. Several powerful individuals as members. Unknown leader. Unknown number and strength of members. Unknown number and strength of minions. Unknown base of operations. Un...", 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 14, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:40Z', 'title': "About the Shiron'Fal IV (Book)", 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/About_the_Shiron%27Fal_IV_(Book)', 'text': "The information that could be gathered about the legion is rather meagre. In Rathleton one of the Shiron'Fal agents unleashed one of its minions, a mummy called the Ravager, to cover his tracks. The i...", 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 15, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:41Z', 'title': 'Archdemons (Book)', 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/Archdemons_(Book)', 'text': 'The principle of opening a gate for a demonic army is the same as summoning a demon. You need to accumulate some critical mass of synergistic energy and open a rift between the worlds. The needed ingr...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 16, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:41Z', 'title': 'Baron Eserak (Book)', 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/Baron_Eserak_(Book)', 'text': 'Baron Eserak was the spiritual leader of a knightly order, devoted to the service of the gods. As a gathering of philosophical and pious men and women, the order often met in debates on spiritual matt...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 17, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:42Z', 'title': 'Demonic Invasions (Book)', 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/Demonic_Invasions_(Book)', 'text': 'We confirm that the Ruthless Seven have occupied the place which is known as Pits of Inferno. With the help of divination, we were able to see that they channelled their dark essence to some remote pl...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 18, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:42Z', 'title': 'Enemies of the True Faith (Book)', 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/Enemies_of_the_True_Faith_(Book)', 'text': 'Enemies of the True Faith First of all there are the heretics. Those are probably the most dangerous enemies because you hardly notice them. They undermine our society and the belief in the gods by th...', 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 19, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:43Z', 'title': "History of the Shiron'Fal (Book)", 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/History_of_the_Shiron%27Fal_(Book)', 'text': "The Shiron'Fal is an organization that seems to predate the dawn of mankind. A time of constant strife and warfare gave birth to a fledgling organisation of dishevelled but powerful individuals. The o...", 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}
  {'source_id': 20, 'created_at': '2026-04-23T23:28:43Z', 'title': "History of the Shiron'Fal II (Book)", 'source_url': 'https://tibia.fandom.com/wiki/History_of_the_Shiron%27Fal_II_(Book)', 'text': "The Shiron'Fal is as old as creation itself. When the first creatures came to be, some of them immediately understood the ultimate paradigm of survival of the fittest. Only the strong shall survive an...", 'payload_json': '{"source": "TibiaWiki/Fandom MediaWiki API"}'}

